# I've successfully moved back to the stone patch. 
# Now, I will attempt to harvest stone from the patch once more, ensuring I am in the correct position to do so.

# I will try to gather a quantity of 20 stone from this patch.
harvested_stone = harvest_resource(Position(x=-14, y=-12), quantity=20)
print(f'Attempting to harvest {harvested_stone} stone from the patch.')

# After harvesting, I will check my inventory to confirm the increase in stone.
print(f"Updated inventory: {inspect_inventory()}")
